OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777903631
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch apologises for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage in social media video
OL,6,FKemi Badenoch has apologised after
OL,7,Ffootage from Bloody Sunday was used in
OL,8,Fa social media clip to criticise a
OL,9,Fbill on legacy issues in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FThe Conservative leader said she did
OL,13,Fnot sign off on the video, and that it
OL,14,Fwas sent out by "very young people".
OL,16,FThe video criticising the Northern
OL,17,FIreland Troubles Bill was posted to
OL,18,FMrs Badenoch's social media channels
OL,19,Fon Tuesday, in which Mrs Badenoch says
OL,20,Fthat the Labour Bill will "drag"
OL,21,FTroubles veterans back to court.
OL,26,@vD@QOUvD@cO]|D@[OU|D@`O]
