OL,3,CKemi Badenoch apologises for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage in social media video
OL,6,FSDLP MP for Foyle Colum Eastwood said
OL,7,Fhe was "shocked" that Mrs Badenoch had
OL,8,Fposted a video "trumpeting the service
OL,9,Fof British soldiers in Northern
OL,10,FIreland using footage from Bloody
OL,11,FSunday".
OL,13,FThirteen unarmed civilians were shot
OL,14,Fdead when members of the Army's
OL,15,FParachute Regiment opened fire on
OL,16,Fcivil rights demonstrators in the
OL,17,FBogside area of Londonderry on January
OL,18,F30 1972.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@PO]pD@POUsD@GO]
